                        <div class="text-center">
                            <a href="/Kurs/Details/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 py-2 shadow-sm">
                                <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>
                                📖 Kurs Hakkında Bilgi Al
